  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "C O P Y",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "[REDACTED] August 12, 1952",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "Air Force Intelligence",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "F. B. I.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "Justice Dept.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Fellow Americans,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "I am writing the same letter to all three Departments.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "On August 1st, I wrote a letter, and mailed it on August 2nd,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "to the Air Force Intelligence telling my views of a flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "saucer. In about four days the physicist [REDACTED] gave out",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "a report of findings identical to my report. Now if I have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "hit upon the meaning of a flying saucer I would like to get",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "the credit for it. I have reason to believe my ideas have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "been hi-jacked. It should be easy to find out. When did",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] start his experiment? Which office did my letter",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "go through? Was my letter placed on file? It had a return",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "address. If you cannot find it that proves it was destroyed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "and the information used.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "I have much better working proof of my theory than",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED], which has been before me all along, until I hit",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "upon the idea.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "The solution should not have been published. There is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "a great deal more to it than that, which I can explain. The",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "idea should have been worked out thoroughly and secretly.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "Rainmakers could probably do a great deal of harm with the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "answer. There is a possibility that it could mean an entirely",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "different type of air warfare. The Air Force could possibly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "use it for defensive warfare. It could lead to man-made flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "saucers which the enemy could use against us.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "Man-made flying saucers possibly could be used in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "conjunction with atom and hydrogen bombs or to destroy them.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "Astronomers could use the information to predict about other",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "planets or planetary warfare. This information could be of use in a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "trip to the moon.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "Does the Air Force wish me to keep my impressions to myself",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "or shall I give a statement to the press? My Country comes first if",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "the information should be kept secret.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "I signed my other letter \"respectfully.\" Then a lady from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "Virginia pays her respects to the Air Force she expects the Air",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "Force to pay its respects right back to her.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "Respectfully,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "[REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "Staunton,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "Virginia",
      "status": "image_matched"
